# Localization

Callstack: 
    Layer 1: 
        initialize: setup files to read and which algorithms to run piecewise for testing
        runMQP: aka Main, takes int structs from initialize and runs all tests specified
        runSDR: ensures that all data is read in correctly and passed to the MCU afterwards
        runMCU: ensures that all needed datatypes from the SDR are appropriately passed to the MCU/ 
            stored
